Package org.eng.aisp

The base package containing some of the core interfaces and classes.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDataWindow<DATA>
    Defines the base functionality for a window of generic data.
    IDataWindowFactory<WINDATA,WINDOW extends IDataWindow<WINDATA>>  
    IDoubleWindow
    Represents a regularly sampled set of data over a time window.
    ILabeledDataWindow<DATA>
    Combines a IDataWindow with a set of labels.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractDataWindow<WINDATA>
    A generic data window providing the base capabilities around time, samples, and independent data for IDataWindow implementations.
    AISPLogger
    Extends the ComponentLogger to define a single PMLLogger root instance.
    AISPProperties
    Defines a component properties search space with the name 'caa'.
    AISPRuntime
    Helper class to allow us to dynamically load classes that may optionally be on the class path.
    DoubleWindow
    Implements a data window holding an array of double values.
    DoubleWindowFactory  
    LabeledDataWindow<WINDATA>  
    LabeledDoubleWindow  
    SensorRecording<WINDOW extends IDataWindow<double[]>>
    Represents the combination of a sensor, a data window together with associated training labels.
    SoundClip
    Stores the raw bits of a sound recording, modeled after PCM.
    SoundClipFactory  
    SoundRecording
    Contains PCM sound data and associated labels.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DataTypeEnum  
    IDataWindow.PadType
    Value passed to IDataWindow.resize(double, PadType).
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AISPException
    A simple extension of Exception to identify CAA-specific exceptions.

Package org.eng.aisp Description

The base package containing some of the core interfaces and classes.
